title: Cosmos ® 4-Port Wall to USB Travel A/C Power Adapter Charger for iPad 2 iPhone 3G 3GS 4 4G ipod shuffle nano classic touch
description:
This 4 Port AC to USB Wall Charger is Light Weight and compact. This is a must have for Home or Travel chargers when needing to charge multiple USB powered Devices. It's easy to carry and free you from worrying about having to charge one device at a time, perfect for the whole family at home or in the hotel room.
